0.text: Innate: Periodically, Maokai empowers his next basic attack to have an  uncancellable windup and  heal him for 5 − 45 (based on level) (+ 4.5% − 11% (based on level) maximum health) after a 0.25-second delay.
0.html: Innate: Periodically, Maokai empowers his next basic attack to have an uncancellable windup and heal him for 5 − 45 (based on level) (+ 4.5% − 11% (based on level) maximum health) after a 0.25-second delay.

1.text: Each time Maokai casts an ability or is struck by an enemy's ability, Sap Magic's cooldown is  reduced by 4 seconds.
1.html: Each time Maokai casts an ability or is struck by an enemy's ability, Sap Magic's cooldown is  reduced by 4 seconds.

2.text: Sap Magic  resets Maokai's basic attack timer, and will not trigger if he is above 95% maximum  health.
2.html: Sap Magic resets Maokai's basic attack timer, and will not trigger if he is above 95% maximum  health.

0.text: Active: Maokai sends a shockwave in the target direction that deals magic damage to enemies and  slows them by 99% for 0.25 seconds.
0.html: Active: Maokai sends a shockwave in the target direction that deals magic damage to enemies and slows them by 99% for 0.25 seconds.

1.text: Enemies near Maokai are also  stunned for 0.5 seconds and  knocked back up to 300 units based on their proximity to him.
1.html: Enemies near Maokai are also stunned for 0.5 seconds and knocked back up to 300 units based on their proximity to him.

0.text: Active: Maokai  dashes to the target enemy while being  untargetable, dealing magic damage and  rooting them for a duration upon arrival.
0.html: Active: Maokai dashes to the target enemy while being untargetable, dealing magic damage and rooting them for a duration upon arrival.

0.text: Active: Maokai  flings a Sapling to the target location, granting  sight of the area.  Once landed, a Sapling remains stationary for 30 seconds or until it reacts to the first nearby visible enemy, chasing them for up to 2.5 seconds. The Sapling explodes upon colliding with an enemy or when it expires, dealing magic damage to nearby enemies upon detonation, capped at 300 against non-champions, and  slowing them by 35% for 2 seconds.
0.html:
Active: Maokai flings a Sapling to the target location, granting sight of the area.

Once landed, a Sapling remains stationary for 30 seconds or until it reacts to the first nearby visible enemy, chasing them for up to 2.5 seconds. The Sapling explodes upon colliding with an enemy or when it expires, dealing magic damage to nearby enemies upon detonation, capped at 300 against non-champions, and slowing them by 35% for 2 seconds.

1.text: A Sapling placed in  brush instead lasts 30 (+ 2.5% bonus health) seconds and deals double damage to struck targets over 3 bursts as well as  revealing them for 3 seconds. The first instance of damage is dealt instantly and the second and third instances occur each 0.75 seconds thereafter. The total damage is capped at 600 against non-champions.
1.html: A Sapling placed in brush instead lasts 30 (+ 2.5% bonus health) seconds and deals double damage to struck targets over 3 bursts as well as revealing them for 3 seconds. The first instance of damage is dealt instantly and the second and third instances occur each 0.75 seconds thereafter. The total damage is capped at 600 against non-champions.

2.text: See Pets for more details about Saplings.
2.html: See Pets for more details about Saplings.

0.text: Active: Maokai summons a colossal wall of five thorny brambles that slowly advances in the target direction, accelerating over time, each stopping when they collide with an enemy  champion.
0.html: Active: Maokai summons a colossal wall of five thorny brambles that slowly advances in the target direction, accelerating over time, each stopping when they collide with an enemy champion.

1.text: Each bramble deals magic damage to enemies hit and  roots them for 0.8 − 2.6 (based on distance traveled) seconds.
1.html: Each bramble deals magic damage to enemies hit and roots them for 0.8 − 2.6 (based on distance traveled) seconds.
